<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20265645">为什么刘秀复国成功，刘备却失败？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="286439" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">这两位都是没落皇族，起兵时无权无势。<br>刘秀是创立了一个新王朝，跟西汉没太大关系。</div>


</div>
